      "text": "あ、そうか……私、お姉ちゃんのためって言いながら\n自分を抑え込もうとしていたんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ you're right… Even though I said it was for my sister‚\nI was trying to hold myself back…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.3976054415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
