      "text": "俺も同じ気持ちだ。どちらか片方だけじゃない\n千紗と沙季が一緒に歌う姿を見たいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel the same way. It's not about one or the other‚\nI want to see both Chisa and Saki singing together.",
        "id": ""
